        "subject": "LU-2272 statahead: sleepable function called under spinlock",
        "message": "LU-2272 statahead: sleepable function called under spinlock\n\nStatahead RPC callback may call ll_intent_drop_lock() which\nwill sleep, thus it should not be called under spinlock.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Idba6395e8d57f1f2dc11ff86ec245adb80caeaa8\n"
      },
